    <ul>
      <li><strong>Patent Prosecution:</strong> Managing the full lifecycle of US utility, design, and trademark applications</li>
      <li><strong>Strategic IP Planning:</strong> Aligning patent portfolios with commercial goals and product roadmaps</li>
      <li><strong>Risk Mitigation:</strong> Authoring Freedom-to-Operate opinions and validity analyses</li>
      <li><strong>Global Coordination:</strong> Working with foreign associates across USPTO, EPO, JPO, and CNIPA</li>
    </ul>

